trans-unit.source: Provides a multilevel switch to control tracing and debug output without recompiling your code.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder flere nivåer bytting til kontrollen sporing og feilsøkingsutdata uten kompilere koden.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource.Switch%2A> property of the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource> class is a SourceSwitch object.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource.Switch%2A>for den <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource>klasse er et SourceSwitch-objekt.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource> </xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource.Switch%2A>

trans-unit.source: The SourceSwitch class provides a <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch.Level%2A> property to test the event level of the switch.
trans-unit.target: Klassen SourceSwitch gir en <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch.Level%2A>til å teste hendelsen krypteringsnivået bryteren.</xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch.Level%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch.Level%2A> property gets or sets the switch's <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceLevel> value.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch.Level%2A>egenskapen henter eller angir du bryteren <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceLevel>verdi.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceLevel> </xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch.Level%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can set the event level of a SourceSwitch through the application configuration file and then use the configured SourceSwitch level in your application.
trans-unit.target: Du kan angi hvilken hendelsen en SourceSwitch via programmets konfigurasjonsfil og bruk konfigurerte SourceSwitch nivået i programmet.

trans-unit.source: Alternatively, you can create a SourceSwitch in your code and set the level directly, to instrument a specific section of code.
trans-unit.target: Du kan også opprette en SourceSwitch i koden og angir nivået direkte til utstyre en bestemt del av koden.

trans-unit.source: To configure a SourceSwitch, edit the configuration file that corresponds to the name of your application.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil konfigurere en SourceSwitch, Rediger konfigurasjonsfilen som tilsvarer navnet på programmet.

trans-unit.source: Within this file, you can set a switch's value or clear all the switches previously set by the application.
trans-unit.target: Du kan angi en bryter verdien i denne filen eller Fjern alle bytter tidligere angitt av programmet.

trans-unit.source: The configuration file should be formatted as shown in the following example.
trans-unit.target: Konfigurasjonsfilen må formateres som vist i eksemplet nedenfor.

trans-unit.source: ``` <switches> <add name="SourceSwitch" value="Verbose"></add> </switches> ``` The switch is used to check whether a trace should be propagated or ignored.
trans-unit.target: ``` <switches> <add name="SourceSwitch" value="Verbose"></add> </switches> ```Bryteren brukes til å kontrollere om en trace være overført eller ignorert.

trans-unit.source: Each <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource> trace method calls the <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch.ShouldTrace%2A> method before calling the listeners.
trans-unit.target: Hver <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource>sporer metodekall den <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch.ShouldTrace%2A>metoden før du kaller lyttere.</xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch.ShouldTrace%2A> </xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource>

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch.ShouldTrace%2A> method returns `false`, the trace is ignored and the trace method exits.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch.ShouldTrace%2A>metoden returnerer `false`sporingen ignoreres og trace-metoden avslutter.</xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch.ShouldTrace%2A>

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch.ShouldTrace%2A> method returns `true`, the trace is passed to the listeners.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch.ShouldTrace%2A>metoden returnerer `true`, sporingen er sendt til lyttere.</xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch.ShouldTrace%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch"></xref> class, specifying the name of the source.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch"> </xref> -klassen som angir kilden.

trans-unit.source: The `name` parameter is used to set the value of the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Switch.DisplayName%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Den `name` parameteren brukes til å angi verdien for den <xref:System.Diagnostics.Switch.DisplayName%2A>egenskap.</xref:System.Diagnostics.Switch.DisplayName%2A>

trans-unit.source: To set the level of your <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch>, edit the configuration file that corresponds to the name of your application.
trans-unit.target: Angi hvor mange din <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch>, Rediger konfigurasjonsfilen som tilsvarer navnet på programmet.</xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch>

trans-unit.source: Within this file, you can add a switch and set its value, remove a switch, or clear all the switches previously set by the application.
trans-unit.target: I denne filen, kan du legge til en bryter og angir verdien, Fjern en bryter, eller Fjern alle bytter satt av programmet.

trans-unit.source: To add a source switch, the configuration file should be formatted as shown in the following example.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil legge til en kilde-bryteren, skal konfigurasjonsfilen formateres som vist i eksemplet nedenfor.

trans-unit.source: The name of the source.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på kilden.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch"></xref> class, specifying the display name and the default value for the source switch.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch"> </xref> klasse, angir visningsnavnet og standardverdien for bryteren kilde.

trans-unit.source: The `displayName` parameter is used to set the value of the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Switch.DisplayName%2A> property; the `defaultSwitchValue` parameter is saved as a field and used to initialize the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Switch.Value%2A> property on first reference.
trans-unit.target: Det `displayName` parameteren brukes til å angi verdien for det <xref:System.Diagnostics.Switch.DisplayName%2A>egenskapen; `defaultSwitchValue` parameteren lagres som et felt og brukes til å starte det <xref:System.Diagnostics.Switch.Value%2A>egenskapen på første referanse.</xref:System.Diagnostics.Switch.Value%2A> </xref:System.Diagnostics.Switch.DisplayName%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > If the switch is defined in a configuration file and the `value` attribute is specified, the configuration file value takes precedence and the `defaultSwitchValue` is ignored.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Hvis bryteren er definert i en konfigurasjonsfil og `value` attributtet er angitt, prioriteres filen konfigurasjonsverdien og `defaultSwitchValue` ignoreres.

trans-unit.source: To set the level of your <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch>, edit the configuration file that corresponds to the name of your application.
trans-unit.target: Angi hvor mange din <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch>, Rediger konfigurasjonsfilen som tilsvarer navnet på programmet.</xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceSwitch>

trans-unit.source: Within this file, you can add a switch and set its value, remove a switch, or clear all the switches previously set by the application.
trans-unit.target: I denne filen, kan du legge til en bryter og angir verdien, Fjern en bryter, eller Fjern alle bytter satt av programmet.

trans-unit.source: To add a source switch, the configuration file should be formatted as shown in the following example.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil legge til en kilde-bryteren, skal konfigurasjonsfilen formateres som vist i eksemplet nedenfor.

trans-unit.source: The name of the source switch.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på bryteren kilde.

trans-unit.source: The default value for the switch.
trans-unit.target: Standardverdien for bryteren.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the level of the switch.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir hvor mange bryteren.

trans-unit.source: This property gets its value from the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Switch.SwitchSetting%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen henter verdien fra det <xref:System.Diagnostics.Switch.SwitchSetting%2A>egenskap.</xref:System.Diagnostics.Switch.SwitchSetting%2A>

trans-unit.source: Setting this property also modifies the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Switch.SwitchSetting%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du setter denne egenskapen også endrer den <xref:System.Diagnostics.Switch.SwitchSetting%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Diagnostics.Switch.SwitchSetting%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > For extensibility, the Level property can be set to any integer, rather than being limited to a <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceLevels> enumeration value.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > For utvidelse, Level-egenskapen kan settes til alle heltall, i stedet for er begrenset til en <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceLevels>opplistingsverdien.</xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceLevels>

trans-unit.source: One of the <xref href="System.Diagnostics.SourceLevels"></xref> values that represents the event level of the switch.
trans-unit.target: Én av de <xref href="System.Diagnostics.SourceLevels"> </xref> verdier som representerer hendelsen bryteren.

trans-unit.source: Invoked when the value of the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Switch.Value*> property changes.
trans-unit.target: Aktiveres når verdien for den <xref:System.Diagnostics.Switch.Value*>egenskapsendringer.</xref:System.Diagnostics.Switch.Value*>

trans-unit.source: The OnValueChanged method converts the new value of the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Switch.Value%2A> property to the integer representation of the matching field in the <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceLevels> enumeration, and then uses this integer to set the <xref:System.Diagnostics.Switch.SwitchSetting%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Metoden OnValueChanged konverterer den nye verdien for det <xref:System.Diagnostics.Switch.Value%2A>egenskapen heltall-representasjon av det tilsvarende feltet i den <xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceLevels>opplisting og bruker denne heltall til å angi det <xref:System.Diagnostics.Switch.SwitchSetting%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Diagnostics.Switch.SwitchSetting%2A> </xref:System.Diagnostics.SourceLevels> </xref:System.Diagnostics.Switch.Value%2A>

trans-unit.source: The new value of <xref:System.Diagnostics.Switch.Value*> is not one of the <xref href="System.Diagnostics.SourceLevels"></xref> values.
trans-unit.target: Den nye verdien for <xref:System.Diagnostics.Switch.Value*>er ikke én av de <xref href="System.Diagnostics.SourceLevels"> </xref> verdier.</xref:System.Diagnostics.Switch.Value*>

trans-unit.source: Determines if trace listeners should be called, based on the trace event type.
trans-unit.target: Bestemmer om sporingslyttere må kalles, basert på hendelsestypen sporingen.

trans-unit.source: This method is called by the `Trace` methods in the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource> class to determine whether listeners should be called to write a trace.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden kalles av den `Trace` metodene i den <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource>klassen for å finne ut om lyttere må kalles for å skrive en sporing.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Application code should not call this method; it is intended to be called only by methods in the <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource> class.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Programmet koden kan ikke kalle denne metoden; den er ment å bare kalles av metodene i <xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource>klasse.</xref:System.Diagnostics.TraceSource>

trans-unit.source: One of the <xref href="System.Diagnostics.TraceEventType"></xref> values.
trans-unit.target: Én av de <xref href="System.Diagnostics.TraceEventType"> </xref> verdier.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""></xref> if the trace listeners should be called; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""></xref>Hvis sporingslyttere må kalles; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.
